{
  "texts": [
    "However, they still perform slightly worse than the smallermodels Alpaca 7B and WizardLM 7B.",
    "Flan-Alpaca and Vicuna 13B perform similarly good.",
    "T5 also shows how much of an effect finetuning has, since the base model scores only 13.6% which means 24% to 30% increase absolute.",
    "One notable exception is mT0 xP3 XXL, which is a multi-lingual version of T5.",
    "It seems that its subpar performance with only 20.9% correct answers is due to the multi-lingual pretraining since BloomZ 7B is also finetuned with xP3 and shows very good results."
  ]
}